* The relation field is set to new record on applied endorsements adding a new record, and removed on cancellation
* Endorsement Step defines if the Endorsement Part can handle several instances.

Version 1.4 - 2015-05-29
* Use rich text format for endorsement summary
* Add void endorsement
* Make endorsement printable
* Add terminate_contract endorsement
* Add extra_data endorsement
* Add endorsement number
* Allow to trigger calculate after application
* Allow to specify restoration order

